# Ignore Rust build targets
/target/

**.csv
**.jsonl
**.txt
**.log
**.h5
**.png
**.env
**.bin
**.npz
**.npy

**/results/
**/wasm-dist/

**/**pycache**

# Local-only research data (kept in-tree for the author, not for git).
# Each subfolder has a README so the user can circle back later.
**/thesis/
/archive/

# ...but the website's thesis-page figures ARE for git. The directory must
# be un-ignored before its contents can be (git stops descending otherwise).
!web/public/figures/thesis/
!web/public/figures/thesis/**

# Ignore verbose docs
docs/